item.title: Jdk development download error
item.dc:creator: @Epic_Steve Epic Steve
item.description:
@Epic_Steve wrote:

The installer for X-Win32 is MSI based and requires Windows Installer Version 3.0 or later to be installed on the target system. Windows Installer Version 3.0 itself requires Windows 2000 SP3 or later in order to operate correctly. Windows Installer Version 3.0 system requirements and a downloadable installer for Version 3.0 can be found on the Windows Installer 3.0 Redistributable page
